column2: select    l.AGCNr as AGCNr, l.RAdeg_OC as ra, l.DECdeg_OC as dec, l.Vhelio as Vhelio, l.Dist as Dist, l.z as HI_z,    N.objID as objID, G.ra as near_ra, G.dec as near_dec,    N.run, N.camcol, N.field, N.rerun, N.type, N.cx, N.cy, N.cz, N.htmID, N.distance, (N.distance*#*l.Dist)/# as distance_Mpc,   Z.z as photo_Near_z into mydb.edge_lsbg_nearby_add_near_radec  from mydb.edge_lsbg_#  l   cross apply dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(l.RAdeg_OC,l.DECdeg_OC,#) N     JOIN photoZ as Z on N.objID = Z.objID     JOIN Galaxy as G on N.objID = G.objID WHERE    Z.z >= (l.z-#*(#+l.z)) and Z.z <= (l.z+#*(#+l.z)) and (N.distance*#*l.Dist)/# <= # order by N.distance
